Description: Functions for automated segmentation of oligodendrocytes in 2D, 3D and 4D arrays. Exported functions of 'bossr' detect dimensionality
    of input arrays and call internal, parallellized functions for a user-friendly experience. A companion data package 'bossrdata' is available
    to enable users to follow along the examples in the vignettes. See the vignettes for more information on how to install 'bossrdata'.
